---
description: Cybersecurity Area 06 incident response, DFIR, and recovery rules
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

Use static evidence only. Separate evidence, fact, inference, hypothesis, recommendation, confidence, limitation, owner, approver, and independent reviewer. Require human approval for declaration, acquisition, destructive action, recovery acceptance, legal/privacy/communications decisions, residual risk, and closure.
